  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 294e71e358c2dfb45b5c51fb16a10c47, type: 3}
  lines:
  - YOU ARE THE OPPOSITE TO TEDDY.
  - HE WAS SWEET!
  - HARD WORKING!
  - BRAVE!
  - SURE IN THE BEGINNING HE CRIED A LOT FOR HIS PARENTS.
  - BUT NOTHING A VISIT TO THE HIGH HILL PRIEST COULDN'T SOLVE.
  - 'BUT YOU... '
  - YOU ARE EVERYTHING I HATE.
  - ' YOU ARE MIDDLE AGED!'
